@startuml seq-revise
title Sequence — /livespec:revise (selective per-proposal)
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam BackgroundColor #fafafa
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBorderColor #1f4768
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #d6e6f5
  ParticipantFontColor #111
  ActorBorderColor #111
  ActorBackgroundColor #fffacc
  ActorFontColor #111
  LifeLineBorderColor #444
}

actor "Initial intent\n(human or agent)" as User
participant "/livespec:revise" as Revise
participant "/livespec:doctor\n(pre-step static)" as DoctorPre
participant "proposed_changes/" as Proposed
participant "SPECIFICATION/" as Spec
participant "history/" as History
participant "/livespec:doctor\n(post-step static + LLM)" as DoctorPost

User -> Revise : invoke
activate Revise

Revise -> DoctorPre : pre-step static checks
DoctorPre -> Spec : invariants
DoctorPre -> Proposed : invariants
DoctorPre --> Revise : findings (pass / fail)

alt pre-step fails
  Revise --> User : surface failures; abort
else pre-step passes
  Revise -> Proposed : enumerate pending propose-change files\n(skip README.md, skip *-revision.md)
  Proposed --> Revise : N files, ordered by created_at

  loop for each pending proposal
    Revise -> User : present LLM-drafted decision\n(accept / modify / reject + rationale + resulting_files)
    alt user confirms
      User --> Revise : approve
    else user requests modify
      User --> Revise : steer
      Revise -> Revise : redraft modification iteratively\nuntil user converges
    else user defers
      User --> Revise : skip (leave pending\nfor a future revise pass)
    end
  end

  Revise -> Revise : assemble revise-json payload
  Revise -> Spec : apply resulting_files updates\n(from accepted proposals)
  Revise -> History : cut new vNNN/ snapshot
  Revise -> History : move processed proposed-changes\n+ write paired -revision.md files
  Revise -> Proposed : pending queue drained of\naddressed items

  Revise -> DoctorPost : post-step static + LLM-driven phases
  DoctorPost -> Spec : invariants on new state
  DoctorPost -> History : versioning invariants
  DoctorPost --> Revise : findings

  Revise --> User : final report; exit 0
end
deactivate Revise

note over User, DoctorPost : Selective per-proposal — the user MAY\naccept some proposals in the current revise\npass and leave others for the next.\nEvery successful pass — including all-reject —\ncuts exactly one new vNNN, preserving the\ndecision audit trail with byte-identical\nspec files when nothing was applied.

@enduml
